Definition: harshly uninviting or formidable in manner or appearance
Example: a dour, self-sacrificing life; a forbidding scowl; a grim man loving duty more than humanity; undoubtedly the grimmest part of him was his iron claw- J.M.Barrie
Synonyms: forbidding, grim, noun, attribute, grimness, harshly, uninviting, or, formidable, in, manner, appearance, a, self-sacrificing, life, scowl, man, loving, duty, more, than, humanity, undoubtedly, the, grimmest, part, of, him, was, his, iron, claw, -, J, M, Barrie
Category: adj.all
